name: Youth (12-17) Intermediate/Advanced Sessions
description:
Our Youth Session offers all junior high and high school students the opportunity to learn choreography and biblical studies. Confirmed choreographers to date (5/9/11) include Amanda Suk, Jacki Lewis, Ellen Kim, Mariel Martin, and Hikari Murakami.

Salt Shakers Dance Mission begins June 13th through July 6th. Youth Sessions meet on Mondays and Wednesdays from 6pm-8pm at Step Off Ministry. All sessions include 8 classes, a pair of shorts, and a t-shirt.

*Please note that July 4th is a Monday, so all classes on this date will be moved to July 1st (Friday).*

8401 Page St. #104
Buena Park, CA 90621

name: Adults (18+) Intermediate/Advanced Session
description:
Our Adults Session offers all graduating high school seniors and older students the opportunity to learn choreography and biblical studies. Confirmed choreographers to date (5/9/11) include Amanda Suk, Jacki Lewis, Ellen Kim, Mariel Martin, and Hikari Murakami.

Salt Shakers Dance Mission begins June 13th through July 6th. Adults Sessions meet on Mondays and Wednesdays from 8:30pm-10:30pm at Step Off Ministry. All sessions include 8 classes, a pair of shorts, and a t-shirt.

8401 Page St. #104
Buena Park, CA 90621
